<HEADLINE> News Items from Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 7 (Xinhua) -- Following are news items from
the Asia-Pacific Desk of Xinhua in Hong Kong Saturday:

hka080720 -- Gold Price in Hong Kong Down
