</P>
<P>
NAIROBI -- Eritrea has officially accepted the proposal on
Technical Arrangements by the Organization of African Unity (OAU)
submitted to Eritrea at the weekend aimed at ending the bloody war
with neighboring Ethiopia.
</P>
<P>
