<HEADLINE> No Pakistani Troops in Afghanistan: Spokesman </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, August 8 (Xinhua) -- Pakistan's Foreign Office
spokesman Tariq Altaf Sunday categorically denied that Pakistan
had any troops in neighboring Afghanistan.
</P>
<P>
