the anti-Taliban opposition that Pakistani troops are fighting in
the Taliban ranks.
</P>
<P>
Referring to the possibility of a U.S. operation against Saudi
dissident Osama bin Laden, Altaf said: "We have nothing to do with
bin Laden, nor will we allow the use of our territory for his
arrest." 
