grant loans if we go ahead with the project," he added.
</P>
<P>
Pacific Transportation Company was granted a concession by the
Lao government last year to build a 14 km railway line from
Vientiane across the Mekong river on the Thai-Lao friendship
bridge to the northeastern gateway province of Nong Khai in
Thailand, according to Gun.
