<HEADLINE> Bus Accident in Bolivia Kills 27 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LIMA, August 7 (Xinhua) -- A bus accident near the Uyuni
community, 800 kilometers south of La Paz, Bolivia, has left at
least 27 dead and 17 injured, police said Saturday.
</P>
